ADDITIONAL PRIVACY NOTICE:

This software is designed to protect user privacy and security. The developers
of this software:

1. Do not collect any personal data or usage analytics
2. Do not store messages or user data on any servers
3. Implement end-to-end encryption for all communications
4. Provide this software as a tool for private communication

Users are responsible for:
- Securing their own devices and private keys
- Understanding the privacy implications of their usage
- Complying with local laws and regulations
- Conducting security audits if using in production environments

CRYPTOGRAPHIC NOTICE:

This software contains cryptographic functionality. The distribution and use
of this software may be subject to export controls in some jurisdictions.
Users are responsible for compliance with applicable laws and regulations.

The cryptographic implementations in this software are based on well-established
protocols and standards, but no cryptographic system is perfect. Users should
consider having the implementation audited by qualified security professionals
before using in high-security environments.

DISCLAIMER:

While this software implements industry-standard cryptographic protocols and
privacy practices, the developers make no guarantees about the absolute
security or privacy of communications. Users assume all risks associated
with the use of this software.

This software is provided for educational, research, and personal use. Users
are encouraged to understand the technology and its limitations before relying
on it for sensitive communications.
